&ldquo;Hey why are all of the images reloading now?&rdquo;
So this past day I&rsquo;ve updated all of the URLs on this website to use the scheme /posts/year/month/article over /posts/article. In addition, I&rsquo;ve also moved all of the images from /static/imgs to /post/year/month/article/gallary. All in all, this means the browser&rsquo;s cached version of this website is no longer valid and now everything has to be reloaded.
I apologize for any inconvinience this may cause.
